title: Rising Moon
description: 97209. Tel. 223-0363. Open: 6:30pm-2:30am daily. "We serve a variety of sandwiches, including a vegie, fruit juices, chips, etc. We have disco dancing Friday and Saturday nites from 9:30pm (50 cent cover charge), 2 pool tables (free pool between 6:30 and 8:30 pm Friday and Saturday nites and all nite Sundays), pin ball, football. We do community benefits, dance marathons and sponsor a softball team. Occasional entertainment. We are a pretty mellow bar during the week and usually crowded at weekends because of the disco.
